{"about_the_game":"This horror game inspired by Chinese folklore offers an enthralling journey through the depths of the Underworld. As you delve deeper, you'll unravel hidden secrets veiled in the darkness.<br><br><strong>Immersive Exploration</strong><br>In a realm shrouded in dread, you'll traverse eerie landscapes, encounter various ghosts, and immerse yourself in their stories.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455040/extras/\u63a2\u7d22.gif?t=1730286993\" /><br><br><strong>Heart-Pounding Survival</strong><br>Surviving in this underworld demands courage and cunning, as danger lurks around every corner. Search for food, build shelters, and craft your own weapons to stay alive.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455040/extras/\u751f\u5b58\u5efa\u9020.gif?t=1730286993\" /><br><br><strong>Dungeons &amp; Gameplay</strong><br>Some ghosts must be vanquished, while others avoided. Utilize the environment and resources, and cooperate with other players to enhance your chances of survival.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455040/extras/\u526f\u672c\u53ca\u73a9\u6cd5.gif?t=1730286993\" /><br><br><strong>Gripping Narrative</strong><br>Immerse yourself in a gripping storyline populated by unique ghosts. Confront your deepest fears and uncover the stories behind the ghosts as you navigate the Underworld.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455040/extras/\u9b3c\u602a\u6545\u4e8b.gif?t=1730286993\" /><br><br><strong>Dynamic Multiplayer</strong><br>Play in an online multiplayer mode and invite friends to embark on this adventure together!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455040/extras/\u591a\u4eba\u6e38\u620f.gif?t=1730286993\" />","achievements":{"highlighted